WebSync by Outer Earth Interactive
Tristan Rice (C) 2013

Setup:
For now, there needs to be a PostgreSQL and Redis server running on the machine. Once those are running, you should be able to run a development server by running:
rackup
and
node web-sockets.js

The production environment is currently setup for use with https://websyn.ca

